column2: Darkside Detective Season 2: A Fumble in the Dark — Part 1 - Little Lost Partner
column7:
Welcome back to The Darkside Detective, with Season 2: A Fumble in the Dark! Re return to find Detective McQueen continuing to search for his best friend and partner Officer Patrick Dooley, who vanished at the end of Season 1. With the help of Inspooktor Extraordinaire Raxa, can we find him, and get back to helping Twin Lakes with its Darkside problems?
